userStories.notes:
Update mapNodeToStep() in serialize.ts to handle the 5 new node types. The switch statement currently handles: reset, write, read, scan, delay. Add cases for: i2c_start, i2c_stop, repeated_start, send_byte, recv_byte.

SendByte serialization: {op: 'send_byte', data: formatHex(node.data.data)}
RecvByte serialization: {op: 'recv_byte', ack: node.data.ack}
Start/Stop/RepeatedStart: just {op: '<name>'}, no additional fields.

Update serialize.test.ts with new test cases. The serializeFlowWithOrder function should also work with the new types.
